data.description: Discover the epitome of luxury living at 6820 Louis Dr., Locust, GA 30248. This 3-story contemporary modern masterpiece on a .5-acre lot boasts meticulous landscaping, sprinklers, and a fenced backyard for privacy. With 6 bedrooms, including an oversized master suite, and a main-floor bedroom, this home is both spacious and flexible.  The main level features a chef's kitchen with top-of-the-line appliances, a dining room, and a living room with a gas log fireplace. Upstairs, enjoy a family room and loft for entertainment, along with a laundry room for convenience.  Luxury details include 10 ft high ceilings on the main level, 9 ft ceilings on the upper level, a double vanity and walk-in his and her closets in the master, and natural gas heating. Security is ensured with smoke detectors, and cable, sewer, and water utilities are included.  The exterior showcases a 4-side brick build, a front porch, and patio, plus a 3-car garage. The community offers a range of amenities through the HOA, including a golf course, lake park, dog park, playground, tennis courts, clubhouse, and pool. Live in comfort and style at this Locust gem!
